The age verification process is conducted through [https://withpersona.com/ Persona] — a third-party verification provider. Users provide a government-issued ID<ref>https://docs.withpersona.com/reference/government-id-verifications Government ID Verifications on ''withpersona.com''; retrieved December 9, 2024.</ref> and use a camera-enabled device, such as a smartphone, or computer with a webcam, to complete the process.